                                         : of the game are not in the start
                                         : directory of the game
                                         :
    > Input/output error - files trouble : HighScore.GWT file is missing
                                         : (which is recreated automatically)
                                         :
    > Unclean little memory troubles     : problems with available memory
                                         :
    > Disk Is Corrupted or Not Validated :
    > Disk Is Write Protected - Retry    : problems with the disk that the
    > 100% Disk Is Full - Retry          : game is memorized
    > No Disk In Drive - Insert          :
    > Sorry! Disk Error                  :
                                         :
    > Med.Library Not Found              : the library file MedPlayer.libs is
                                         : not present in the system directory
                                         : LIBS, the music of the game they can
                                         : not be reproduced
                                         :
    > Help file not found - I / O Error  : the ReadMe file that corresponds to
                                         : language choice is not in the start
                                         : directory of the game
                                         :
    > INTERNAL ERROR CODE xxx            : internal error and corresponding
                                         : 'xxx' code for debugging
